4:T65e,<p><b>Moisturising Body Cream Body Care Juvena</b> is a quality product designed for discerning individuals who look after their appearance and are looking for the best cosmetics to enhance their beauty. If you are one of them, the 100% original <b>Juvena products</b> are made for you.</p>
<ul>
<li>Gender:
<ul>
<li>Lady</li>
<li>Unisex</li>
<li>Feminine</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>Capacity: 200 ml</li>
<li>Ingredients:
<ul>
<li>Propylheptyl caprylate</li>
<li>Punica granatum fruit extract</li>
<li>Pyrus cydonia seed extract</li>
<li>Simmondsia chinensis (jojoba seed oil)</li>
<li>Sodium hydroxide</li>
<li>Stearic acid</li>
<li>Tetrasodium glutamate diacetate</li>
<li>Tocopherol</li>
<li>Tocopheryl acetate</li>
<li>Water (Aqua)</li>
<li>Xanthan gum</li>
<li>Alpha-isomethyl ionone</li>
<li>Benzyl salicylate</li>
<li>Butylene glycol</li>
<li>Butyrospermum parkii (shea) butter</li>
<li>Caprylyl glycol</li>
<li>Carbomer</li>
<li>Cetearyl ethylhexanoate</li>
<li>Citronellol</li>
<li>Ethyl linoleate</li>
<li>Fragance (parfum)</li>
<li>Glyceryl caprylate</li>
<li>Glyceryl stearate se</li>
<li>Hydrogenated polyisobutene</li>
<li>Limnanthes alba (meadowfoam) seed oil</li>
<li>Limonene</li>
<li>Linalool</li>
<li>Palmitic acid</li>
<li>Panthenol</li>
<li>Phenethyl alcohol</li>
<li>Phenoxyethanol</li>
<li>Glycerin</li>
<li>Cetyl alcohol</li>
<li>Geraniol</li>
<li>Ascorbyl palmitate</li>
<li>Lecithin</li>
<li>Alcohol denat (ethyl alcohol)</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>Texture: Cream</li>
<li>Type:
<ul>
<li>Pan</li>
<li>Normal Skin</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>Volume: 100 ml</li>
<li>Quantity: 1 ud</li>
<li>Suitable for: Dry Skin</li>
</ul>
